### Users module — manual verification
### All routes require auth. Run login in auth.http first to get an access token.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@accessToken = paste-access-token-here

### Get my profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update my profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "phone": "9800000000"
}

### List my addresses
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Add an address (first one becomes default automatically)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Home",
  "fullName": "Test Customer",
  "phone": "9800000000",
  "addressLine": "Lazimpat, Ward 2",
  "city": "Kathmandu",
  "district": "Kathmandu",
  "latitude": 27.7172,
  "longitude": 85.3240,
  "isDefault": true
}

### Update an address
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/addresses/REPLACE_ADDRESS_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "Lalitpur",
  "district": "Lalitpur"
}

### Set an address as default
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/addresses/REPLACE_ADDRESS_ID/default
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Delete an address
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/addresses/REPLACE_ADDRESS_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
